metadata.description:
La Rumba is a collaboration between Xcelencia and Dance music producer Gianni Blu. Collectively both artists have over 100M streams and joined forces to release their new Latin House single combining musical fusions from different parts of the world. 

We got inspired by the recent surge in Latin House music taking the industry by storm. We were sitting on this single for some time waiting for the right moment. Releasing this song is one of our top priorities going into 2023 and we have a few exciting plans for this one..

Artist: Xcelencia, Gianni Blu
Production: Gianni Blu
Artwork: Luis Avivv
metadata.name: La Rumba #1
